{"ts":1779829469768,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"Your UTR availability monitor is running smoothly. Here's the current state:\n\n**Status:** Sold Out (unchanged since May 16)  \n**Last Check:** May 26, 2:04 PM PT  \n**Next Check:** May 26, 3:04 PM PT  \n**Schedule:** Hourly, with 5-minute stagger  \n**Model:** Correctly set to haiku-4.5\n\nThe job recovered from earlier timeout errors and is now executing successfully. It's tracking state properly and ready to detect when availability changes.\n\n**One thing to note:** Delivery mode is currently set to `none`, so even when the device becomes available, no notification will be sent. Would you like me to:\n\n1. **Enable notifications** — set up a delivery channel (email, Slack, Discord, etc.) so you get alerted when it's back in stock\n2. **Adjust the schedule** — change from hourly to more/less frequent checks\n3. **Test the monitor** — manually trigger a check now to verify everything's working\n4. **Leave it as-is** — just keep tracking state silently\n\nWhat works best for you?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"7743756f-c0f1-4a08-9ce5-ed8f08b7e2c9","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:7743756f-c0f1-4a08-9ce5-ed8f08b7e2c9","runAtMs":1779829451263,"durationMs":18497,"nextRunAtMs":1779833051246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":561,"output_tokens":990,"total_tokens":300}}
