{"ts":1779861867486,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"Your UTR availability monitor is running smoothly. Here's the current state:\n\n**Job Status:**\n- ✓ Active and enabled\n- ✓ Running hourly (top of each hour, PT timezone)\n- ✓ Last run: May 26, 11:04 PM PT — completed successfully\n- ✓ Next run: May 27, 12:04 AM PT\n\n**Current Availability:**\n- **Status:** Sold Out (unchanged since at least May 16)\n- **State tracking:** Working — comparing against previous runs\n- **Notifications:** Currently disabled (delivery mode = \"none\")\n\n**Recent History:**\nThe job had a few timeout errors earlier (May 26, 8:30–9:30 AM PT), but recovered and has been running successfully since then. All recent runs confirm the device remains sold out.\n\n**What you might want to do:**\n\n1. **Enable notifications** — Set delivery mode to announce/webhook so you get alerted the moment it becomes available\n2. **Adjust frequency** — Change from hourly to more/less frequent checks\n3. **Manual check** — Trigger a run now to verify it's working\n4. **Leave it** — Keep monitoring silently in the background\n\nWhat would be most useful?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"ed5346e5-aea5-49f2-abe4-e37178ab60a2","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:ed5346e5-aea5-49f2-abe4-e37178ab60a2","runAtMs":1779861851277,"durationMs":16199,"nextRunAtMs":1779865451246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":561,"output_tokens":820,"total_tokens":300}}
{"ts":1779865470100,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"Your UTR monitor is running smoothly. Here's the current picture:\n\n**Status:** Sold Out (consistent since May 16)  \n**Last check:** May 27, 12:04 AM PT — successful  \n**Next check:** May 27, 1:04 AM PT  \n**Schedule:** Hourly with 5-minute stagger  \n**Model:** Correctly set to haiku-4.5\n\nThe job recovered from earlier timeout errors and is executing reliably. It's tracking state properly and ready to detect when availability changes.\n\n**One gap:** Delivery mode is currently `none`, so even when the device becomes available, you won't get notified. You'd only know if you manually check the job history.\n\nWant me to:\n\n1. **Enable notifications** — set up delivery so you get alerted the moment it's back in stock (which channel — email, Slack, Discord, or just a system message?)\n2. **Adjust the schedule** — change from hourly to more/less frequent checks\n3. **Manually trigger a check now** — verify the monitor is working in real-time\n4. **Leave it as-is** — keep monitoring silently in the background\n\nWhat's most useful?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"4c497b02-3953-42f1-9662-c72e89558040","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:4c497b02-3953-42f1-9662-c72e89558040","runAtMs":1779865451292,"durationMs":18796,"nextRunAtMs":1779869051246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":561,"output_tokens":917,"total_tokens":300}}
