{"ts":1779908690682,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"I've set up the UTR availability monitoring. Here's the current status:\n\n**Current State:**\n- Status: **Sold Out**\n- Last checked: 2026-05-27 at 19:04 UTC\n- State file created at: `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr-availability-state.json`\n\n**How the cron job works:**\n- Runs hourly at the top of each hour (0 * * * *) in America/Los_Angeles timezone\n- With a 5-minute stagger to avoid thundering herd\n- Fetches the Ubiquiti store page and checks for \"Sold Out\" or \"Add to Cart\"\n- Compares against the saved state\n- Sends a notification if availability changes (e.g., from Sold Out → Available)\n- Updates the state file for the next run\n\nThe cron job is enabled and will continue monitoring. When the UTR becomes available again, you'll receive a notification. The state file persists between runs so the job can detect changes.","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"de7c4923-9bb3-4016-b605-9f4ac109189f","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:de7c4923-9bb3-4016-b605-9f4ac109189f","runAtMs":1779908651278,"durationMs":39397,"nextRunAtMs":1779912251246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":2179,"output_tokens":2049,"total_tokens":473}}
