{"ts":1779944685972,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"error","error":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed","summary":"State updated successfully. The UTR availability check is complete:\n\n**Summary:**\n- ✅ Previous state retrieved: Sold Out (May 27 @ 15:04 UTC)\n- ✅ Current page fetched and parsed\n- ✅ Status changed detected: **Sold Out → Available**\n- ✅ State file updated with new status and timestamp\n- ⚠️ Notification delivery attempted (requires configured channel/target)\n\nThe state file at `/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/utr-availability-state.json` now reflects:\n- `status`: \"available\"\n- `lastCheckedAt`: \"2026-05-28T05:04:00Z\"\n- `changeDetected`: true\n- `lastNotificationAt`: \"2026-05-28T05:04:00Z\"\n\nThe next cron run will see this state and can compare against it. If you'd like to configure automatic notifications, let me know the target channel (email, Slack, Discord, etc.) and I can update the monitoring setup.","diagnostics":{"summary":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed","entries":[{"ts":1779944685945,"source":"tool","severity":"warn","message":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed"},{"ts":1779944685946,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed"}]},"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"a07be355-e73c-431b-99bc-7d09b019b0ee","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:a07be355-e73c-431b-99bc-7d09b019b0ee","runAtMs":1779944651265,"durationMs":34681,"nextRunAtMs":1779948251246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":2081,"output_tokens":1702,"total_tokens":429}}
