{"ts":1780088668730,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"Your UTR Availability Monitor is running smoothly. Here's the current picture:\n\n**Status Summary:**\n- **Device:** Ubiquiti Travel Router — **Sold Out**\n- **Last checked:** 1:04 PM PT today (May 29)\n- **Monitoring:** Active, running hourly\n- **Consecutive successful runs:** 50+\n- **Model:** Correctly configured for haiku-4.5 ✓\n\n**The Gap:**\nThe job detects state changes perfectly, but `delivery.mode` is set to `\"none\"`. This means even when the device becomes available, you won't get notified—you'd only know by checking the job history manually.\n\n**What would be useful?**\n\n1. **Enable notifications** — I can update the job to alert you when availability changes. Which channel?\n   - System message (announce to your session)\n   - Email\n   - Slack/Discord webhook\n   - Telegram\n\n2. **Manually trigger a check now** — Verify it's working in real-time\n\n3. **Adjust the schedule** — Change from hourly to a different interval\n\n4. **Leave it as-is** — Keep monitoring silently\n\nWhat's your preference?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"77134b3a-c356-4f87-8c84-29ed1e90e88b","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:77134b3a-c356-4f87-8c84-29ed1e90e88b","runAtMs":1780088651271,"durationMs":17448,"nextRunAtMs":1780092251246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":563,"output_tokens":876,"total_tokens":302}}
