{"ts":1780283067974,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"ok","summary":"The UTR Availability Monitor check is complete. Here's the status:\n\n**Current State:** Sold Out\n\nThe page fetch was successful and clearly shows \"Sold Out\" for the Ubiquiti Travel Router (UTR) at $79.00.\n\n**What happened:**\n- ✓ Successfully fetched the product page\n- ✓ Detected \"Sold Out\" status\n- The device is currently unavailable\n\n**For the next cycle:**\nThe cron job is configured to run hourly at the top of each hour (0 * * * *) with a 5-minute stagger window. The next check will run at 9:00 PM Pacific time.\n\nIf you'd like to:\n- **Get notified when it becomes available** — I can set up a notification delivery mode on the cron job\n- **Check more frequently** — I can adjust the schedule\n- **Store state persistently** — I can create a knowledge page to track availability changes between runs\n\nWould you like me to make any of these adjustments?","deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"3286938f-3b6a-4de2-8468-060cc3d6b84f","sessionKey":"agent:dj:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:3286938f-3b6a-4de2-8468-060cc3d6b84f","runAtMs":1780283051274,"durationMs":16689,"nextRunAtMs":1780286651246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":892,"output_tokens":1023,"total_tokens":334}}
