{"ts":1780369489620,"jobId":"587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7","action":"finished","status":"error","error":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed","summary":"State change detected and recorded ✓\n\n**Availability Monitor Report:**\n- **Previous state**: available\n- **Current state**: sold_out\n- **State file updated**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/cron-state/utr-state.txt`\n\nThe Ubiquiti Travel Router is now **Sold Out** (detected change from available).\n\nNote: This cron job has `delivery.mode: \"none\"` configured. To enable notifications on state changes, you can update the cron job with a delivery channel:\n\n```bash\ncron update --jobId 587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7 \\\n  --delivery.mode announce \\\n  --delivery.channel <channel-id> \\\n  --delivery.to <recipient>\n```\n\nOr set a webhook destination for state-change alerts.","diagnostics":{"summary":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed","entries":[{"ts":1780369489584,"source":"tool","severity":"warn","message":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed"},{"ts":1780369489584,"source":"agent-run","severity":"error","message":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed"}]},"deliveryStatus":"not-requested","delivery":{"intended":{"channel":"last","to":null,"source":"last"},"fallbackUsed":false,"delivered":false},"sessionId":"054a737a-4622-47d1-a6c4-0acf4c8a33af","sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:587736e6-c589-4867-9b1e-ac921b4e5fa7:run:054a737a-4622-47d1-a6c4-0acf4c8a33af","runAtMs":1780369451266,"durationMs":38326,"nextRunAtMs":1780373051246,"model":"claude-haiku-4.5","provider":"kiro","usage":{"input_tokens":2105,"output_tokens":1891,"total_tokens":425}}
